    <briefdescription>
<para>Element-by-element clipping of a value. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The value is constrained between 2 bounds.</para>
<para>There are separate functions for floating-point, Q7, Q15, and Q31 data types. </para>
